@node "Futur" "The Twinlight Zone"
@{u}@{fg shine}Future@{uu}@{fg text}

WebMaker will be WYSIWYG ... Drag & Drop ŕ gogo... to insert pictures,
texts, sounds, links !!!

1.x releases will be not WYSIWYG and without preview window.
2.x releases will have full preview window.
3.x releases will be WYSIWYG.

Create is so easy.

I'm planning : 
- NetWeb , a Web Navigator but independent multi-taking multi-windows
- maybe a HTML datatype ... *8) NetSurf only with MultiView !!! 
  Too easy, isn't?
@endnode

@node "Contact" "Contacting the author ..."
@{u}@{fg shine}Contact@{uu}@{fg text} 
Webmaker is ShareWare, but 100% usable, if you want to send something : 
hard (I'm looking for an accelerator board for my poor A2000, 
and an graphic board, soft (Genius PD You have made), or anything.

